    "body": "<!-- deep-review-sentinel -->\n\n<!-- coder-agents-review-bot-begin -->\n**Chat:** Review in progress | [View chat](https://dev.coder.com/agents/fb7352b4-4fda-46e8-8cde-666e1e561d47)\n**Requested:** 2026-06-08 10:59 UTC by @johnstcn\n\n<!-- coder-agents-review-bot-end -->\n\n<!-- deep-review-begin -->\n<!-- dr-header-begin -->\n**deep-review** v0.7.1 | Round 1 | [`8ae1a5c..eeb6fd6`](https://github.com/coder/coder/compare/8ae1a5c766125934f5f51644537dbf0299bc297b...eeb6fd64aa387cc15ac6f97a86f94b9ccd449e7c)\n<!-- dr-header-end -->\n<!-- dr-status-begin -->\n<!-- dr-status-end -->\n<!-- dr-posted-begin -->\n**Last posted:** Round 1, 5 findings (1 P3, 3 Nit, 1 Note), COMMENT. [Review](https://github.com/coder/coder/pull/26132#pullrequestreview-4448959879)\n<!-- dr-posted-end -->\n<!-- dr-inventory-begin -->\n<details>\n<summary>Finding inventory</summary>\n\n# Finding inventory\n\n## Findings\n\n| # | Sev | Status | Location | Summary | Round | Reviewer | Posted |\n|---|-----|--------|----------|---------|-------|----------|--------|\n| CRF-1 | Note | Open | testutil/http.go:13 | Sibling duplication: roundTripper adapter copies in coderdtest.go:1778 and oidctest/idp.go:1792 | R1 | Netero, Robin | Yes |\n| CRF-2 | P3 | Open | PR description | Plan describes non-existent base code state (transportErrorFunc, function adapter) | R1 | Mafu-san (P2\u2192P3) | Yes |\n| CRF-3 | Nit | Open | codersdk/workspaces_test.go:276 | srvURL no longer refers to a server; baseURL matches the actual role | R1 | Gon | Yes |\n| CRF-4 | Nit | Open | codersdk/workspaces_test.go:280 | xerrors.New when errors.New would avoid a new import | R1 | Ging-Go | Yes |\n| CRF-5 | Nit | Open | testutil/http.go:13 | Missing compile-time interface assertion var _ http.RoundTripper | R1 | Ryosuke | Yes |\n| CRF-6 | Nit | Dropped by orchestrator (PR title correctly omits scope; commit ephemeral for squash-merge) | commit message | Commit scope codersdk doesn't cover testutil/ | R1 | Leorio | No |\n| CRF-7 | P3 | Dropped by orchestrator (PR description contains the diagnosis; will survive squash-merge) | commit message | Empty commit body | R1 | Leorio | No |\n\n## Round log\n\n### Round 1\nPanel. 1 P3, 3 Nit, 1 Note. 2 dropped. Reviewed against 8ae1a5c766..eeb6fd64aa38.\n\n</details>\n<!-- dr-inventory-end -->\n<!-- dr-about-begin -->\n<details>\n<summary>About deep-review</summary>\n\n**CRF** = Coder Review Finding (P0-P4, Nit, Note)\n\n| Reviewer | Focus |\n|----------|-------|\n| Bisky | tests |\n| Chopper | ops/errors |\n| Churn-guard | change verification |\n| Ging | language modernization |\n| Gon | naming |\n| Hisoka | edge cases |\n| Killua | perf |\n| Kite | change integrity |\n| Knov | contracts |\n| Knuckle | SQL |\n| Kurapika | security |\n| Law | decomposition |\n| Leorio | docs |\n| Luffy | product |\n| Mafu-san | process |\n| Mafuuu | contracts |\n| Melody | dispatch/pairing |\n| Meruem | structural |\n| Nami | frontend |\n| Netero | mechanical checks |\n| Pariston | premise testing |\n| Pen-botter | product gaps |\n| Razor | verification |\n| Robin | duplication |\n| Ryosuke | Go arch |\n| Takumi | concurrency |\n| Zoro | shape |\n\n</details>\n<!-- dr-about-end -->\n<!-- deep-review-end -->\n\n> \ud83e\udd16 Managed by [Coder Agents](https://coder.com).",
